    image: '/images/evidence/namecheap-template-library.svg'
  },
  {
    date: 'Dec 2, 2024',
    title: 'Customization Limits Reality Check',
    description: 'Tried to customize a generated site: change colors beyond presets, upload custom fonts, modify section layouts, add custom CSS.',
    finding: 'Customization is very limited. Colors: 12 preset palettes, no custom hex codes. Fonts: 8 font pairs, no custom uploads. Layouts: locked sections, can\'t move elements between them. Custom CSS: not available on any plan. After 90 minutes, I had a site that looked slightly different from the template but still generic. If you want design control, this isn\'t the tool. If you want "set and forget" basic web presence, it works but you\'ll look like everyone else using Namecheap templates.',
