  },
  {
    date: 'Dec 9, 2024',
    title: 'Pricing vs Value Analysis',
    description: 'Analyzed Namecheap\'s pricing ($1.49-9.99/mo) vs feature set. Compared value proposition against Hostinger ($2.99-7.99/mo) and GoDaddy ($9.99-16.99/mo).',
    finding: 'Namecheap\'s pricing is competitive but not a standout value. Cheapest plan ($1.49/mo with 2-year commitment) gets you a basic builder and domain connected. That\'s cheaper than Hostinger ($2.99/mo) but you get less: Hostinger has AI Writer, Image Generator, better templates. At $9.99/mo, Namecheap is the same price as GoDaddy but with fewer features and worse templates. The pricing looks attractive until you compare what you get. Verdict: good enough if you want everything on one bill, but not a deal.',
