            <strong>Template count:</strong> ~40<br>
            <strong>Modern designs:</strong> &lt; 10%<br>
            <strong>Portfolio options:</strong> Virtually none
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-yellow-500 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">Domain Integration (The Only Real Advantage)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            If you buy domains from Namecheap, they connect instantly to the builder. This is convenient. But here's the math: Domain connection saves you 5 minutes of setup ONCE. You'll spend hundreds of hours in the builder. Is 5 minutes worth settling for worse tools?
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            <strong>Setup time saved:</strong> 5 minutes once<br>
            <strong>Builder usage:</strong> Hours daily<br>
            <strong>ROI:</strong> Negative trade-off
          </p>
        </div>

        <div class="border-l-4 border-green-500 pl-6">
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-2">What Namecheap Does Best (Honest Assessment)</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-700 mb-3">
            Domain registration. Namecheap is excellent at domainsâ€”competitive pricing, clean interface, good support. The website builder exists to upsell domain customers. Buy domains from Namecheap. Build websites with Framer, Hostinger, or Wix. Don't let "convenience" trap you in mediocre tools.
          </p>
          <p class="text-sm text-gray-600">
            <strong>Domains:</strong> Excellent (9/10)<br>
            <strong>Website builder:</strong> Mediocre (5/10)<br>
            <strong>Recommendation:</strong> Split services
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mb-12">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 mb-6">What I Tested</h2>
      <div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg">
        <ul class="space-y-3">
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-green-500 mt-1">âœ“</span><span>Website builder interface</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-green-500 mt-1">âœ“</span><span>AI text generation</span></li>
          <li class="flex items-start gap-3"><span class="text-green-500 mt-1">âœ“</span><span>Template library</span></li>
